              <p class="text-muted  mb-1" style="font-size:13px;">[ Markings have several different colors. Standard markings can have different, similar colors ]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 px-2">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2">▫ Quilted Markings ▫</p>
              <p class="text-muted  mb-1" style="font-size:13px;">[ Cryptie has two separate marking and pelt in splotches along their body ]</p>
            </div>
           </div></div>
         </div>

        <div class="row no-gutters"><div class="col-12"><h3 class="text-uppercase my-3" style="color:#de59f0">Myhtical Fur/Pelt Traits</h3>
          <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="col-md-4 px-2">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2">▫ Transparent Skin ▫</p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1" style="font-size:13px;">[ Skin is somewhat see-through, or completely translucent, allowing sight of the Cryptie's internals. All guts and organs are the same color as their blood. ]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 px-2">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2">▫ Material Skin ▫</p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1" style="font-size:13px;">[ Skin is made of a non-natural material, such as fabric or stone. This can effect the Cryptie's mobility or durability. Innards are all unaffected ]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 px-2">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2">▫ Sparkle Fur  ▫</p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1" style="font-size:13px;">[ Fur sheds glittery particles ]</p>
            </div>
           </div></div>
